OL,7,FA driver who drank 10 pints before
OL,8,Fgetting behind the wheel, crashing
OL,9,Finto multiple vehicles and leaving a
OL,10,Fwoman in a coma has been jailed.
OL,12,FLeigh Brean was on a night out for
OL,13,Ffive hours before he decided to drive
OL,14,Fa Volkswagen Tiguan with two
OL,15,Fpassengers along the A38 near Bristol,
OL,16,Fon 28 October 2023.
