OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FBrean, from Lawrence Road, Wrington,
OL,8,Fovertook two 'bendy buses'
OL,9,F(articulated buses) in a stretch of
OL,10,Froad where overtaking is banned,
OL,11,Fcolliding with one of them in the
OL,12,Fprocess.
OL,14,FHe then collided with a Fiat 500
OL,15,Ftravelling in the opposite direction,
OL,16,Fseriously injuring both people inside.
