OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA woman in the Fiat was placed in a
OL,8,Fcoma for two months following the
OL,9,Fcrash. She suffered traumatic injuries
OL,10,Fto her arm, leg and brain, and doctors
OL,11,Fdecided they needed to amputate her
OL,12,Farm at the elbow.
OL,14,FThe other victim also suffered
OL,15,Fsignificant internal bleeding and
OL,16,Fbruising.
