OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FWhen officers were called to the
OL,8,Fcrash, 44-year-old Brean refused to
OL,9,Fcomplete a roadside test despite
OL,10,Fofficers suspecting of drinking. He
OL,11,Falso pleaded his innocence and
OL,12,Finsisted he was not the driver.
OL,14,FHe later pleaded guilty to causing
OL,15,Fserious injury by dangerous driving
OL,16,Fand for failing to provide a specimen.
OL,18,FJudge: 'The victim's life is now a
OL,19,Fshadow of that which it once was and
OL,20,Fshe will never recover fully'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
