OL,4,Ccausing 'unimaginable harm' to woman
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FJudge Martin Picton jailed Brean for
OL,8,Fthree years and two months, and banned
OL,9,Fhim from driving for 11 years and
OL,10,Fseven months, at Bristol Crown Court
OL,11,Fon 7 January.
OL,13,FDuring the sentencing, Judge Picton
OL,14,Fsaid: "Your decision to drive when
OL,15,Fdrunk has resulted in the infliction
OL,16,Fof unimaginable harm to (the victim).
OL,18,F"She was someone full of energy and
OL,19,Fenthusiasm for life and a successful
OL,20,Fbusinesswoman. She was physically very
OL,21,Factive both at work and at leisure.
OL,26,@xD@YpmxD@dpn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
