OL,3,CDriver who drank 10 pints before
OL,4,Ccausing 'unimaginable harm' to woman
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"As a result of your actions, her life
OL,8,Fis now a shadow of that which it once
OL,9,Fwas and she will never recover from
OL,10,Fthe harm you caused when you chose to
OL,11,Fdrive dangerously and when heavily
OL,12,Fintoxicated.
OL,14,F"Your remorse will provide no comfort
OL,15,Fto the female victim, her family or
OL,16,Fher partner who has also suffered harm
OL,17,Fas a result of being in the car at the
OL,18,Ftime of the collision."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
