OL,7,FThe family of one of his victims - who
OL,8,Fasked not to be identified - added
OL,9,Fthat they were pleased with the
OL,10,Fconviction.
OL,12,FThey said: "The best part of this
OL,13,Fsentence was the length of the driving
OL,14,Fban.
OL,16,F"We are aware of how many careless
OL,17,Fdrivers there are on the road and the
OL,18,Ffact that there is one less on the
OL,19,Froad is a very welcome prospect.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
