OL,7,F"We hope that other judges in the
OL,8,Ffuture may make note of this aspect of
OL,9,FBrean's sentence."
OL,11,FPolice: 'This shows how the impact of
OL,12,Fone decision can have a life-long
OL,13,Fimpact'
OL,15,FDC Victoria Anderson, Avon and
OL,16,FSomerset Police's officer on the case,
OL,17,Fpraised the victims and families for
OL,18,Fshowing "incredible strength and
OL,19,Fresilience in the face of such
OL,20,Fadversity".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
