OL,7,FShe added that they "now have to live
OL,8,Fwith the impact of one individual's
OL,9,Fcomplete recklessness."
OL,11,FDC Anderson concluded: "This case has
OL,12,Fshown how the impact of one decision
OL,13,Fcan have a life-long impact on all
OL,14,Fthose involved."
